{"tid":2233496,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰城圍板改裝空勤人員集合處　國泰：為試行電子健康護照準備","createTime":"2020-10-07T07:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T05:52:53.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c93e1d4be76d541c55b9b0b1afe9b247b9d74d57","tid":2233496,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2770000/2770648/293_cx_ka_aircraft_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2770000%2F2770648%2F293_cx_ka_aircraft_1024.jpg&h=e4a7f38e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰航空 （00293） 本季交代集團重組方案，內部員工近期屢流傳裁員相關安排，國泰多次向員工重申目前未有確實交代重組安排日期。國泰員工最新再流傳圖片，指出國泰城內的空勤人員集合處已經改裝，以圍板劃成獨立區域，並聲稱國泰會議室已經準備就緒，憂慮公司快將裁員。<br />\n<br />\n國泰回應查詢時解釋，有關改裝是為試行「電子健康護照（CommonPass Digital Health Pass）」準備，現時已在圍板加上相關計劃的指示牌，釋除員工疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空、美國聯合航空將會率先以「電子健康護照」試營倫敦、香港、紐約、新加坡之間的航線，有關計劃由世界經濟論壇（WEF）、瑞士非牟利機構CommonPass倡導，讓跨境出行人士以資料保密方式申報新冠病毒檢測結果，而美國海關、疾病管制與預防中心（CDC）都會觀察試飛結果。"},{"pid":"225353b3f491f2525850bcdfd40e14426b2daf42","tid":2233496,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2770000/2770648/crewlounge_01_groupphoto_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2770000%2F2770648%2Fcrewlounge_01_groupphoto_1024.jpg&h=24657432&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41dad195847c7766986c1899dce74c7e8bcbe87a","tid":2233496,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"去完外國再番香港再播再封<br />\n無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9add3cb0f44d1ad02c7ee013435b60ee63a269fe","tid":2233496,"uid":105490,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"無健康碼唔比旅行<br />\